   &UR; BUSINESS DAY _ (Moved in ``f'' category)  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   BIOTECH-STORYTELLING (St. Louis) _ Jeremy Rifkin never misses a
chance to argue that the biotechnology industry is leading the
world toward environmental and social disaster. If he thinks it
will help slow the industry down, he is quick to file lawsuits and
promote boycotts or moratoriums. Last week, the activist happily
trekked to the headquarters of Monsanto Co. here to offer up his
vision of the future. By Barnaby J. Feder.
