<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-24 03:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7725 &Cx1f; ttd-z
r w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GORE-CALIFORNIA-SFCHR     06-24 0761
