Emmy-winning HBO stand-up show, ``Bring the Pain,'' established
Chris Rock as a talent bigger and better than any of his peers, a
voice too strong, too funny for his fame to be limited to his race,
his generation. Now here comes ``Chris Rock: Bigger &AMP; Blacker,'' a
new stand-up show that will play on HBO next month. By MIKE
McDANIEL
