   FOOD (``d'' category)
</P>
<P>
   POTATO-SALAD (Albany, N.Y.) _ Who says making potato salad means
peeling potatoes? And who decreed you have to make enough for an
army? And what law requires potato salad to contain mayonnaise?
Thanks to the grab-and-go nature of products in the supermarkets,
making potato salad is now fast, easy and flavorful. By RUTH
FANTASIA.
</P>
