<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-24 15:06 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8119 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-EERIE-FUNERAL-FISK-10     06-24 2141
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-EERIE-FUNERAL-FISK-1000&AMP;add-INDEPENDENT-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE AGONY _ AND IRONY _ OF BOBAN JELICIC'S DEATH  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
