 (ATTN. EDITORS: FOR THOSE DESIRING A SHORTER VERSION, THIS ARTICLE
OFFERS TWO EDITOR-FRIENDLY OPTIONAL TRIMS, TOTALING 550 WORDS _ AT
1,000 AND 1,900. TOTAL OF STORY WITHOUT TRIMS IS 2,000.)  
  
