<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-24 15:06 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8120 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-RUN-TRACK-FIELD-HNS &LR;      06-24 0525
