<HEADER>
A8125 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FINANCIAL-NYT-BUDGET &LR;      06-24 0406
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FINANCIAL-NYT-BUDGET </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   &UR; FOR FRIDAY AMs  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Financial stories from The New York Times News Service for
newspapers of Friday, June 25. &LR;
</P>
<P>
   MICROSOFT-TRIAL (Washington) _ The final day of testimony. By
Joel Brinkley.
</P>
