again,'' one Belgian youth said Thursday after getting sick from
drinking a Coca-Cola 10 days ago. That is exactly the sentiment
that the Coca Cola Company fears most in Belgium and many other
parts of Europe after the biggest recall in its 113-year history.
By Alan Cowell.
</P>
