million or two Albanian Kosovar deportees. NATO _ which does not
mean the United States alone _ has now intervened deeply enough to
commit itself for the long term to peace in the Balkans. Anything
less fails to justify the West's resort to arms.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (William W. Hagen is professor of history at the University of
