<P>
   The undated story BC-ONBUSINESS-COLUMN-BOS, sent earlier today,
is KILLED. Do not use this story.
</P>
<P>
   Repeat: BC-ONBUSINESS-COLUMN-BOS (f) is KILLED.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;
</P>
