<P>
   NEW YEAR-DESTINATIONS &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ If you're like me, you made a New Year's resolution
last year not to put off making plans for New Year's this year. And
if you're like me, you probably still haven't even thought about
making those plans. But don't panic. You're not alone. A lot of
folks have yet to make plans to party like it's 1999. And despite
all the dire predictions made by compulsive types who booked their
tickets to the Y2K bash two years ago, there are still plenty of
options available for the New Year's procrastinator. By TODD CAMP.
Story has moved in ``t'' travel category. &QL; 
