   END OF PAGE
</P>
<P>
   RAC-NASCAR-SPENCER _ After a frustrating start in which he lost
his sponsor and dropped to the middle of the pack in points, Jimmy
Spencer says last week's top five finish has rejuvenated his
campaign. (Schlabach, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 18.
</P>
