</P>
<P>
   BKN-SPURS _ Friday night could be the night that San Antonio
explodes into the post-game pandemonium of an NBA championship.
This game day story will say just how prepared the Alamo city is
for victory. What are the fans expected to do once the last seconds
tick off the clock with a Spurs win. And how about after the game
night commotion dies down? Will there be a ticker-tape parade along
the Riverwalk? A downtown jubilee? (Harmon, Austin
American-Statesman).
</P>
<P>
   BKN-WNBA-TAJ _ Taj McWilliams, who plays for the WNBA's Orlando
Miracle, will be inducted into the St. Edward's Athletic Hall of
Fame on Saturday. A reader on McWilliams and how she's faring in
the pros. (Halliburton, Austin American-Statesman).
</P>
