   HOCKEY
</P>
<P>
   HKN-DRAFT-THRASHERS _ ATLANTA _ Advance on the NHL expansion
draft to stock the Atlanta Thrashers. The Thrashers will select 26
players, one from each team but Nashville. The draft will be held
in Boston. (Schultz, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 20.
</P>
<P>
   HKN-DRAFT-EUROPE _ The top four players in this year's NHL
amateur draft and 12 of the top 20 may be Europeans. Is this
further evidence of a shift in hockey talent away from U.S. and
Canada? Do Olympic results, where both U.S. and Canada faltered and
Czech beat Russia in the finals, mean anything? (Schultz, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 25.
</P>
