struggled for 25 years to represent workers at six Fieldcrest
Cannon plants has claimed victory after a two-day election. By
David Firestone.
</P>
<P>
   MEDICARE-PREMIUMS (Washington) _ House Democrats are beginning
to express fears that a plan being drafted by President Clinton to
revamp Medicare could have negative consequences. By Robert Pear.
