7:30 p.m. PDT. 
Long Beach Press-Telegram. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBN-DODGERNOTES (Los Angeles) _ Notebook from the Dodgers-Padres
game. 
By Brian Dohn. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
