Mariners at 7:05 p.m. PDT. 
By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBA-ANGELNOTES (Seattle) _ Notebook from the Angels-Mariners. 
By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
RAC-HORSE-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ Weekly horse racing column. 
By Kevin Modesti. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 

